{"tid":1442990,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[長期置頂] 毋忘721元朗襲擊","createTime":"2019-08-11T06:02:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T14:59:42.000Z","uid":161684,"like":110,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":80,"replies":[{"pid":"17b60c9fb313d333196fce4627a2cc1d6f25697a","tid":1442990,"uid":161684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:02:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WVcTCzE4nHM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DWVcTCzE4nHM&d=haqyWHVU0l66G8glzozbU9MQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=47308f8c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WVcTCzE4nHM</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nfzQW1VpJW4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DnfzQW1VpJW4&d=haqyWHVU0l66G8glzozbU9MQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=a79fbac1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nfzQW1VpJW4</a><br />\n<br />\n試下完整咁睇一次條片 即使唔忍心睇都唔好停頓<br />\n因為每一棍都係打落你同我身上<br />\n無論政治取態 無論社會地位<br />\n你行過地鐵站 就要畀人兇 就要畀人打<br />\n而警察失縱 行過唔理 警署閂門 捉完人唔起訴<br />\n我地同呢個偽政權仲有咩好傾呀<br />\n一早超越晒底線喇<br />\n<br />\n中國共產黨 特區政府 警察 黑社會<br />\n僅僅二十年時間 破壞盡香港百年來建立嘅文明<br />\n而家搞到出街著咩色都要諗呀<br />\n而家香港搞到生番地方咁呀<br />\n所以恕我講句<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"dd4472e8d4c897846c1bcfed07602f4669cd2f3d","tid":1442990,"uid":161684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:02:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/元朗站惡煞手持木棒打人-市民記者被追打受傷-未見警員執法/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E7%AB%99%E6%83%A1%E7%85%9E%E6%89%8B%E6%8C%81%E6%9C%A8%E6%A3%92%E6%89%93%E4%BA%BA-%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E8%A2%AB%E8%BF%BD%E6%89%93%E5%8F%97%E5%82%B7-%E6%9C%AA%E8%A6%8B%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E5%9F%B7%E6%B3%95%2F&d=haqyWHVU0l66G8glzozbU9MQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=55ff812f\" data-ef-url=\"https://